sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant React as HeartButton
    participant Zustand as Store
    participant Action as likeNote()
    participant DB as Database

    Note over React,Zustand: Optimistic UI updates instantly

    User->>React: Click Heart
    React->>Zustand: optimisticToggleLike
    Zustand-->>React: Update UI (Count++)
    React->>Action: call likeNote()
    Action->>Action: Verify Auth
    Action->>DB: BEGIN TX
    Action->>DB: Insert note_like
    Action->>DB: Update leaderboard_points
    Action->>DB: Insert transaction
    Action->>DB: COMMIT
    Action->>Action: Award Badges
    Action->>Action: Create Notification
    Action-->>React: Return Success

    alt Error or Duplicate
        Action-->>React: Return Error
        React->>Zustand: Revert Like (Count--)
        React->>User: Show Error Toast
    end
